FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Got questions? We've got answers. Here's what you need to know about our food delivery service.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: How does the food delivery app work?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app allows you to browse local restaurants, select your favorite dishes, place an order, and have food delivered right to your doorstep. Simply download the app, create an account, and start ordering!
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Delivery fees vary based on your location and the restaurant you're ordering from. The exact fee will be displayed before you complete your order. We also offer a subscription service for frequent users that includes free delivery on eligible orders.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: How long does delivery usually take?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Delivery times depend on factors such as distance, traffic, and restaurant preparation times. On average, most orders arrive within 30-45 minutes. You can track your order in real-time through the app.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Can I schedule an order for later?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Yes! Our app allows you to schedule orders in advance. Simply select your desired delivery time when placing your order, and we'll make sure it arrives at the specified time.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: What if there's an issue with my order?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: If you experience any problems with your order, please contact our customer support team through the app or website. We're committed to ensuring your satisfaction and will work to resolve any issues promptly.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does the food delivery app work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app connects you with local restaurants, allowing you to browse menus, place orders, and track your delivery in real-time. Simply select your items, choose a payment method, and wait for your delicious meal to arrive at your doorstep.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Delivery fees vary depending on the restaurant's distance and current demand. The exact fee will be displayed before you complete your order. We also offer a subscription service for frequent users that provides free delivery on eligible orders.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: How long does delivery usually take?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Delivery times typically range from 30-45 minutes, depending on the restaurant's preparation time and your location. You can track your order's progress in real-time through the app, including estimated arrival time.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: What if there's an issue with my order?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: If you encounter any problems with your order, such as missing items or incorrect dishes, please use the 'Help' section in the app to report the issue. Our customer support team is available 24/7 to assist you and ensure a satisfactory resolution.
